Package sudoku.ui

Interface Summary
Command Command interface for concrete commands to implement.
 

Class Summary
AboutDialog Creates the window for the about information
AddGuessCommand Created when the user enters a number runs the execute portion
ChoosePuzzleDialog Allows the user to choose a puzzle.
ClearCommand Will clear the screen
CommandInvoker Invokes a command.
ConnectionDialog Creates the window for start up options.
Field Field is a JTextField that knows its position in a grid.
HowToDialog Creates the window for How to play Sudoku.
IconSetter Used to access images from jar file.
OptionsDialog Displays player options and allows them to be changed.
PlayerDataModel Used to display the player's statistics to the screen.
PrintUtility This is code that I got from the internet it implements the abstract Printable class, and allows for this to be easily printed.
RemoveGuessCommand When the user removes a number.
Sudoku The MAIN Sudoku class, initializes the GUI (SudokuFrame) and allows global access to it.
SudokuFrame The class that instantiates all GUI components.
SudokuMenu Class for all the menu items in the Sudoku frame.
SudokuPanel The main panel for Sudoku.
TestModule Encapsulates all tests created for this module.
